<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.193991>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9 – 10. Chlaenius pectinipes Bates, 1892. 9) Holotype, male, dorsal view. 10) Holotype, male, ventral view. FIGURES 11 – 12. Chlaenius schillhammeri Kirschenhofer, 2003. 11) Holotype, female, dorsal view. 12) Paratype, female, ventral view. Scale line = 5.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/193991/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.193992>
    dc:description "FIGURES 13 – 15. Chlaenius freyi Jedliċka, 1960. 13) Holotype, male, dorsal view. 14) female, in IOZ, dorsal view. 15) female, in IOZ, ventral view. Scale line = 5.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/193992/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.193989>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 4. Chlaenius piligenys sp. nov. 1) Holotype, male, dorsal view. 2) Holotype, male, ventral view. 3) Paratype, female, dorsal view 4) Paratype, female, ventral view. Scale line = 5.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/193989/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.193990>
    dc:description "FIGURES 5 – 8. Chlaenius rotundithorax sp. nov. 5) Holotype, male, dorsal view. 6) Holotype, male, ventral view. 7) Paratype, female, dorsal view. 8) Paratype, female, ventral view. Scale line = 5.0 mm" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/193990/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.193996>
    dc:description "FIGURES 29 – 34. Pronotum of Chlaenius (Chlaenioctenus) species. 29) C. piligenys, holotype. 30) C. rotundithorax, holotype. 31) C. pectinipes, holotype. 32) C. freyi, holotype. 33) C. freyi, IOZ. 34) C. schillhammeri, holotype. Scale line = 1.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/193996/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.193997>
    dc:description "FIGURES 35 – 39. Elytral intervals of Chlaenius (Chlaenioctenus) species. 35) C. piligenys, holotype. 36) C. rotundithorax, holotype. 37) C. pectinipes, holotype. 38) C. freyi, holotype. 39) C. schillhammeri, holotype. Scale line = 1.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/193997/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.193994>
    dc:description "FIGURES 20 – 25. Heads of Chlaenius (Chlaenioctenus) species. 20) C. piligenys, holotype, white arrow indicating the pubescence on gena. 21) C. rotundithorax, holotype. 22) C. pectinipes, holotype. 23) C. freyi, holotype. 24) C. freyi, IOZ. 25) C. schillhammeri, holotype. Scale line = 1.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/193994/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

